<b>阿閦婆</b>(ā chù pó)(QYS. ʔâ tṣhjuk buâ)　　(a transliteration of Skt. <i>akṣobhya</i>(a certain high number))　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  11.937.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  11.810.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">53b29.我先供養佛已，得<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">解一切衆生語言</span>陀羅尼，復聞是《法華經》八百千萬億那由他、甄迦羅、頻婆羅、<span style="color: #8B0000">阿</span><span style="color: #8B0000">閦</span><span style="color: #8B0000">婆</span>等偈(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 409.6.akṣobhya~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 125c7.而常心中無瞋恚(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> -)怒; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 218; ; </span></p>

