藏竄(cáng cuàn)　“hides”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  9.594.; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.979d(魏志、晉書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">14a25.舍宅　忽然火起　…………　諸鬼神等　揚聲大叫　雕鷲、諸鳥　鳩槃荼等　周章惶怖　不能自出　惡獸、毒蟲　<span style="color: #8B0000">藏</span><span style="color: #8B0000">竄</span>孔穴(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 85.10-; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  77a10; </p>

