常耳
常耳(cháng ěr)　“ordinary ears, natural ears”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.736.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.455.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">48a6.三千大千世界中一切内外所有諸聲，雖未得天耳，以<span style="text-decoration: underline">父母所生</span>清淨<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">常</span><span style="color: #8B0000">耳</span></span>，皆悉聞知(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 357.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">prākṛta</span>~  ... <span style="text-decoration: underline">śrotrêndriya</span>~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 119b22.<span style="text-decoration: underline">肉耳根</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">48a10.父母所生耳　清淨無濁穢　以此<span style="color: #8B0000">常</span><span style="color: #8B0000">耳</span>聞　三千世界聲(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 357.10.śrotrêndriya~ ... prākṛtaka~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .śrotrêndriya~ ... prākṛtika~; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  119b29; </p>

