惡道(è dào)　“evil destinies, evil states of existence (of sentient beings)”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://惡趣">惡趣</a>(è qū), <a href="bword://三惡道">三惡道</a>(sān è dào), <a href="bword://四惡道">四惡道</a>(sì è dào); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.559a(六祖壇經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 4.1097c(大藏法數); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">10b12.當來世惡人　聞佛説一乘　迷惑不信受　破法墮<span style="color: #8B0000">惡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 58.14.naraka~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 73a18.地獄; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">15c29.常處地獄　如遊園觀　在餘<span style="color: #8B0000">惡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>　如己舍宅　駝驢猪狗　是其行處　謗斯經故　獲罪如是(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 96.11.apāya-bhūmi~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 79b9.勤苦惡趣; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">24a1.衆生聞此法　得道若生天　諸<span style="color: #8B0000">惡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>減少　忍善者增益(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 171.2.āsura-kāya~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 90c9.阿須倫身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">24c9.世尊未出時　十方常暗(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 闇)冥(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 瞑)　三惡道增長　阿修羅亦盛　諸天衆轉減　死多墮<span style="color: #8B0000">惡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 177.2.durgati~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 91b6.惡趣; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">24c14(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 177.7.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 91b11.<i>do.</i>)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">26a15.如來亦復如是，今爲汝等作大導師，知諸生死煩惱<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">惡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>險難</