及於(jí yú)　“and, as well as”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://及以">及以</a>(jí yǐ), <a href="bword://及與">及與</a>(jí yŭ); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.636.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.684.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">57c4.卽時，<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">觀世音</span>菩薩愍諸四衆<span style="color: #8B0000">及</span><span style="color: #8B0000">於</span>天、龍、人、非人等，受其瓔珞(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 446.7.ca; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  129c17; </p>

