嫉恚
嫉恚(jí huì)　“hatred, aversion”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  4.396.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.746.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">38a25.我滅度後　若有比丘　能演説斯　《妙法華經》　<span style="text-decoration: underline">心無<span style="color: #8B0000">嫉</span><span style="color: #8B0000">恚</span></span>　諸惱障礙　亦無憂愁(<a href="bword://J">J</a>.  惱)(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 284.11.<span style="text-decoration: underline">an-īrṣuka</span>~(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> jātīrṣuka~); <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .aniṣkuha (?); <a href="bword://F">F</a>. .aniṣkuha (?); <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 108c25.<span style="text-decoration: underline">無所悕望</span>; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>.  168; ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">38b21.若欲説是經　當捨<span style="color: #8B0000">嫉</span><span style="color: #8B0000">恚</span>慢　諂([= KS<i> etc.</i>] ← 謟[= G, J])誑邪僞心　常修質直行(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 286.13.īrṣyā~; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>.  169; ; </span><a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 109a22.嫉妬; </p>

