<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">集一切功<b>德</b></span>(jí yī qiè gōng dé)　　(name of a <i>samādhi</i>)　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">55a-1(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 424.5.Sarva-puṇya-samuccaya; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 127a28.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">等集衆德</span>)</p>

幾所
幾所(jǐ suǒ)　“how many? how much?”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 4.449a(漢書); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 4.545c(漢書); <a href="bword://GHX">GHX</a>. 273(漢書、風俗通義); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">46b-7.若有善男子、善女人，聞是《法華經》，隨喜者，得<span style="color: #8B0000">幾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">所</span>福？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 345.2.kiyat~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .kevat~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 118a3.何; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">46b-4.世尊滅度後　其有聞是經　若能隨喜者　<span style="text-decoration: underline">爲</span>得<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">幾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">所</span></span>福？(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 345.6.<span style="text-decoration: underline">kiyat</span>~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">kevat</span>~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 118a5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">爲</span>(得)<span style="text-decoration: underline">何</span>(福祐)？; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">58b12.若善男子、善女人有能受持《法華經》者，若讀誦通利，若書寫經卷，得<span style="color: #8B0000">幾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">所</span>福？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 395.3.kiyat~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .kevat~; <a href="bword://Lü">Lü</a>. B-17 (Verso).6.ketakaṃ; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 129c29.(獲福)如何; </p>

