<b>旣</b>已(jì yǐ)　“already”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 4.657b(莊子); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.712c(列子); <a href="bword://Wáng Yúnlù 1997">Wáng Yúnlù 1997</a> : 185(晉詩 <i>etc.</i>); <a href="bword://Wáng Yúnlù 1999">Wáng Yúnlù 1999</a> : 280(宋詩 <i>etc.</i>); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">10b18.汝等<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">旣</span><span style="color: #8B0000">已</span>知</span>　諸佛世之師　隨宜方便事　無復諸疑惑　心生大歡喜　自知當作佛(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 59.5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">vijāniyā</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .vijāniya; <a href="bword://D2">D2</a> <i>etc.</i> vijāniya; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 73a24.<span style="text-decoration: underline">了</span>; </p>

