<b>䶩</b>齧(jì niè)　“chews, champs”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 12.1459a(起世經、法華經); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  12.1111.; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://IQ(Xy)">IQ(Xy)</a>. 83a-1f., <a href="bword://Kuījī">Kuījī</a>  758c9f., <a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 486c-5; ; </span><span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Kuījī">Kuījī</a>  758c9f.; ; </span><span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 486c-5; ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">13c29.狐、狼、野干　咀嚼踐蹋　<span style="color: #8B0000">䶩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">齧</span>死屍　骨肉狼藉(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 83.11.vibhakṣayantaḥ; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .bhakṣayaṃti; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 76c3.咀嚼; </p>

加趺
<b>加趺</b>(jiā fū)　“crosses one’s legs”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://結加趺坐">結<span style="color: #8B0000">加</span><span style="color: #8B0000">趺</span>坐</a>(jié jiā fū zuò); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.775.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.373.; <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; <a href="bword://IQ(Xy)">IQ(Xy)</a>.  78b10; <a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 483a-7f.; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.455a. 跏趺(佛典); ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">4c1.佛説此經已　卽於法座上　<span style="color: #8B0000">加</span>(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 跏)<span style="color: #8B0000">趺</span>坐三昧　名<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">無量義處</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 23.11.paryaṅka bandhitva; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 66c10.加(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 跏)趺; </p>

