結加趺坐
<b>結加趺坐</b>(jié jiā fū zuò)　“sits cross-legged”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://加趺">加趺</a>(jiā fū); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 9.808b.結跏趺坐(晉代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 8.1033d.結跏趺坐(慧琳音義); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">2b9.佛説此經已，<span style="color: #8B0000">結</span><span style="color: #8B0000">加</span>(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 跏)<span style="color: #8B0000">趺</span><span style="color: #8B0000">坐</span>，入於<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">無量義處</span>三昧，身心不動(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 5.9.paryaṅkam ābhujya; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .paryaṃkaṃ baddhvā; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 63b26.加趺; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">4a10.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">日月燈明</span>佛　………　説是經已，卽於大衆中<span style="color: #8B0000">結</span><span style="color: #8B0000">加</span><span style="color: #8B0000">趺</span><span style="color: #8B0000">坐</span>，入於<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">無量義處</span>三昧，身心不動(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 19.13.paryaṅkam ābhujya; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. 19.13.badhvā; <a href="bword://H3">H3</a> [267].bandhitvā; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  66a19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">22b22.其佛………如是一小劫乃至十小劫，<span style="color: #8B0000">結</span><span style="color: #8B0000">加</span>(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 跏)<span style="color: #8B0000">趺</span><span style="color: #8B0000">坐</span>，身心不動。而諸佛法猶不在前(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 159.5.(sakṛd)-vartana~(<i>v.ll.</i> -baddha~,-vaddha~) paryaṅka~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .(sakṛd)-vartana~-buddha~[<i>read</i> baddha~]) paryaṅka~; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  89a5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">33a18.諸寶樹下皆有師子之座，高