林野(lín yě)　“forest, wood”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 4.802a(西晉代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 6.234c(西晉代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">14c25.如來已離　三界火宅　寂然閑居　安處<span style="color: #8B0000">林</span><span style="color: #8B0000">野</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 90.1.pavana~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 77c29.林樹; </p>

伶俜
<b>伶俜</b>(líng píng)　“wanders around, roams”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.1269a(玉臺新詠); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.680d(古樂府); <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://IQ(Xy)">IQ(Xy)</a>. 85c11f.; ; </span><span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 488c8f.; ; </span><span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Kuījī">Kuījī</a>  776c8f.; ; </span><span class="xr">cf.  also <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.380b. 竛竮(梁代); ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">17b11.此是我子，我之所生。於某城中，捨吾逃走，<span style="color: #8B0000">伶</span><span style="color: #8B0000">俜</span>(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 竛竮; <a href="bword://J">J</a>.  跉俜; cf. <a href="bword://Jízàng">Jízàng</a>  553b10. 跉跰; <a href="bword://Dàoshēng">Dàoshēng</a>  405a15. 跉跰)辛苦五十餘年(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://K">K</a>.  108.9; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 80c22.流迸; </p>

