<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">魔</span>賊(mó zéi)　“marauders (headed by) <i>Māra</i>”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  12.475.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  12.705.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">54c12.汝今已能破諸<span style="color: #8B0000">魔</span><span style="color: #8B0000">賊</span>，壞生死軍。諸餘怨敵皆悉摧滅(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 420.3.-Māra-pratyarthika~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 126c19.衆魔; </p>

