n-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 395.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">kiyat</span>(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i>-) .... <span style="text-decoration: underline">bahu puṇya prasavet</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .***; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  130a4; </p>

