褰縮(qiān suō)　“shrunk, wrinkled”<i> or</i>　“(the lips are) pursed”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 9.122b, s.v. 褰④(宋代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.255.; <a href="bword://Kuījī">Kuījī</a>  837a2 ;  =  <a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 491c3; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">47a14.是人功德，轉身得與陀羅尼菩薩共生一處，利根智慧，百千萬世終不瘖瘂，………　脣不下垂，亦不<span style="color: #8B0000">褰</span><span style="color: #8B0000">縮</span>，不麁澁，不瘡胗，亦不缺壞，亦不喎(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 咼)斜(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 邪)，不厚不大，亦不黧黒，無諸可惡(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 350.8.abhyantara-(oṣṭha~) ... prasārita-(oṣṭha~; <i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> viprasārita-oṣṭha~); not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  118b22; </p>

鉛錫
鉛錫(qiān xī)　“lead”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 11.1237b(晉代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 11.516c(後漢書); <a href="bword://IQ(Xy)">IQ(Xy)</a>. 80c-6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">8c29.若人爲佛故　建立諸形像　………　或以七寶成　鍮石(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 鉐)、赤白銅　<span style="text-decoration: underline">白鑞及<span style="color: #8B0000">鉛</span><span style="color: #8B0000">錫</span></span>　鐵、木及與泥　或以膠漆布　嚴飾作佛像　如是諸人等　皆已成佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 51.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">sīsa</span>~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 71b11.銅; </p>

