乾闥婆
乾闥婆(qián tà pó)(QYS. gjän3 thât buâ)　　(a transliteration of Skt. <i>gandharva </i>(heavenly musicians, a kind of demigods))　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://乾闥">乾闥</a>(qián tà); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.797a(維摩詰經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.403b(大智度論); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">2a26.有四<span style="color: #8B0000">乾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">闥</span><span style="color: #8B0000">婆</span>王───<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">樂</span>乾闥婆王、<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">樂音</span>乾闥婆王、<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">美</span>乾闥婆王、<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">美音</span>乾闥婆王───各與若干百千眷屬倶(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 4.15.(catur~)gandharva-kāyika-(devaputra~); <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 63b15.<b>淨身</b>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">6b24.其求緣覺者　比丘、比丘尼　諸天、龍、鬼神　及<span style="color: #8B0000">乾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">闥</span><span style="color: #8B0000">婆</span>等　相視，懷猶豫　瞻仰兩足尊(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 35.2.gandharva~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 68c29.揵沓; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">12a8.天、龍、夜叉、<span style="color: #8B0000">乾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">闥</span><span style="color: #8B0000">婆</span>、阿修羅、迦樓羅、緊那羅、摩睺羅伽等大衆見<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">舍利弗</span>於佛前受阿耨多羅三藐三菩提記，…………(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 69.5.-gandharva-; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 74c26.揵沓惒; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">48a1(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 356.9.gandharva-; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 119b19.揵沓和)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">59a14(≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 399.6.kumbhāṇḍa-; ＝ <a href="bword://D1">D1</a> .gandharva-; ＝ <a href="bword://D2">D2</a> .gandharva-; ＝<a href="bword://K’">K’</a> <i>etc.</i> gandharva-; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .***; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 130b13.香音 ; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>.  238; ; </span>)</p>

