<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">清淨</span>(qīng jìng)　　(name of a <i>samādhi</i>)　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">55a-1(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 424.5.Prasādavatī; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 127a29.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;"><b>喜信淨</b></span>)</p>

清涼
清涼(qīng liáng)　“tranquil, cool, tranquillity”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 5.1317b(百喩經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 7.78d(論衡); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">19c18.譬如大雲　起於世間　遍覆一切　<b>惠</b>([= KS <i>etc.</i>]←慧)雲含潤　電光晃曜　雷聲遠震　令衆悦豫　日光掩蔽　地上<span style="color: #8B0000">清</span><span style="color: #8B0000">涼</span>　靉靆垂布　如可承攬(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 126.5.śītala~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 83c29.陰涼; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">21a5.(the <i>Buddha</i>) 若知我深心　見爲授記者　如以甘露灑　除熱得<span style="color: #8B0000">清</span><span style="color: #8B0000">涼</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://K">K</a>.  147.6; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  87a8; </p>

