曲<b>戾</b>(qū lì)　“crooked”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 5.566b(山海經注、法華經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.960a(宋代); <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://IQ(Xy)">IQ(Xy)</a>. 89b-3; ; </span><span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Kuījī">Kuījī</a>  837a9; ; </span><span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 491c9; ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">47a16.是人功德，轉身得與陀羅尼菩薩共生一處，利根智慧，百千萬世終不瘖瘂，……… 鼻不匾㔸，亦不<span style="color: #8B0000">曲</span><span style="color: #8B0000">戾</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 350.9.vakra-(nāsa~); <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .vaṃka-(nāsa~); <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 118b23.偏戾; </p>

