<b>軀命</b>(qū mìng)　“life”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.712b(晉代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 10.976c(元代); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">13a4.是長者但令諸子得免火難，全其<span style="color: #8B0000">軀</span><span style="color: #8B0000">命</span>，非爲虛妄(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 76.10.jīvita~; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  75c6; </p>

