三十三天
<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">三十三天</span>(sān shí sān tiān)　“the Heaven of the Thirty-three (Gods)”(Skt. <i>Trā̌yastriṃśa</i>)　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://忉利">忉利</a>(dāo lì); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.171a(大智度論); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.142d(佛地經論); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">32b23.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;"><span style="color: #8B0000">三</span><span style="color: #8B0000">十</span><span style="color: #8B0000">三</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span></span>雨天曼陀羅華，供養寶塔(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 240.1.trāyastriṃśatkāyikā  devaputrā; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. . trayastriṃśā devaputrā; <a href="bword://Wi">Wi</a>. 80. trayastriṃśā devaputrā; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 102c1.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">忉利</span>諸天; </p>

