三世界(sān shì jiè)　“the triple universe”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://三界">三界</a>(sān jiè); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.188.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.153.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">53c21.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">一切衆生憙見</span>菩薩見佛滅度，………　收取舍利，作八萬四千寶瓶，以起八萬四千塔，<span style="text-decoration: underline">高<span style="color: #8B0000">三</span><span style="color: #8B0000">世</span><span style="color: #8B0000">界</span></span>，表刹莊嚴，垂諸幡蓋，懸衆寶鈴(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 412.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">yāvad brahmalokam uccaistvena</span>; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 126a1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">高至</span><span style="text-decoration: underline">梵</span><span style="text-decoration: underline">天</span>; </p>

