色像
色像(sè xiàng)　“form, shape, figure, appearance”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://色相">色相</a>(sè xiàng); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  9.15.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  9.511.; <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">50a1.若聲聞、辟支佛、菩薩、諸佛説法，皆於身中現其<span style="color: #8B0000">色</span><span style="color: #8B0000">像</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 370.7.ātma-bhāva-; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 121c27.已威光; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">50a5.若持《法花》者　其身甚清淨　如彼淨琉璃　衆生皆憙見　又如淨明鏡　悉見諸<span style="color: #8B0000">色</span><span style="color: #8B0000">像</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 370.12.bimba~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 122a4.面像; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">50a10.若持《法花》者　其身甚清淨　…………　三千世界中　一切諸群萌　天、人、阿修羅　地獄、鬼、畜生　如是諸<span style="color: #8B0000">色</span><span style="color: #8B0000">像</span>　皆於身中現(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 371.2.pratibimba~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 122a8.面顏容; </p>

