宿福慶
宿福慶(sù fú qìng)　“merit, accumulated in some previous existence”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.1527.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.1044.; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.947a.福慶(漢代); ; </span><span class="xr">cf.  also <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v. <b>宿福</b>(sù fú); ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">23c23.今佛出於世　………　爲衆生之父　哀愍饒益者　我等<span style="color: #8B0000">宿</span><span style="color: #8B0000">福</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慶</span>　今得値世尊(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 170.4.puṇya~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 90b29.福; </p>

宿命
