我身
<b>我身</b>(wǒ shēn)　“I myself, I”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://汝身">汝身</a>(rŭ shēn); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 5.212a(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.20c(唐代); <a href="bword://Gurevich 1974">Gurevich 1974</a> : 60~61(太子須大拏經 <i>etc.</i>); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">4b16.爾時<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙光</span>菩薩豈異人乎？　<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>是也。<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">求名</span>菩薩汝身是也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 22.10.ahaṃ; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 66b22.吾; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">5b15.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙光</span>法師者　今則<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>是(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 28.2.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 67c14.我身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">34a7.我滅度後　誰能護持　讀説斯經？　今於佛前　自説誓言　…………　<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">多寶</span>如來　及與<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>　所集化佛　當知此意(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 252.7.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 104b24.我身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">51a22(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 381.13.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 123b9.我身)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">51b24(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 384.8.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 123c18.我身)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">61b17.得是陀羅尼故，無有非人能破壞者，亦不爲女人之所惑亂。<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>(<i>i.e.</i><i>Samantabhadra</i>)亦自常護是人(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://K">K</a>.  476.8; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  133b2; </p>

烏摩勒伽
烏摩勒伽(wū mó lè qié)(QYS. ʔuo muâ lək gja)　　(a transliteration which corresponds with BHS.<i> omāraka</i>(a kind of demon))　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.75.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.411.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">59b7.若夜叉，若羅刹，若餓鬼，若富單那，若吉遮，若毘陀羅，若犍馱，若<span style="color: #8B0000">烏</span><span style="color: #8B0000">摩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">勒</span><span style="color: #8B0000">伽</span>，若阿跋摩羅，若夜叉吉遮，……………亦復莫惱(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 401.5.omāraka~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 130c3.顚鬼; </p>

