無等等(wú děng děng)　“unparalleled, supreme” (a literal translation of BHS. <i>asama-sama </i>　“unparalleled”)　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.137.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.446.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">58b7.佛説是《普門品》時，衆中八萬四千衆生皆發<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span>阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 456.8.asama-sama~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 129c25.至無等倫(?); </p>

