現前(xiàn qián)(1)       　“now, present, at present; in one’s presence”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://現在">現在</a>(xiàn zài); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 4.580a(宋代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 7.922b(清代); </p>① 　“now, present, at present”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">7c5.若有比丘實得阿羅漢，若不信此法，無有是處。除佛滅度後、<span style="color: #8B0000">現</span><span style="color: #8B0000">前</span>無佛(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://K">K</a>.  43.15; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 69c29.面現; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">28b26.我今當<span style="color: #8B0000">現</span><span style="color: #8B0000">前</span>次第與授(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 受)阿耨多羅三藐三菩薩記(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 206.9.etarhi saṃmukhībhūta~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 96c10.現在目下; </p>② 　“in one’s presence”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">45c11.如是僧坊、堂閣若干百千萬億其數無量。以此<span style="color: #8B0000">現</span><span style="color: #8B0000">前</span>供養於我及比丘僧(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 339.6.saṃmukhaṃ; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  117a26; </p>

