痟痩
<b>痟</b>痩(xiāo shòu)　“wasted, emaciated”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.320a(晉代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.1177.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">15c19.其有誹謗　如斯經典　………　若得爲人　………　口氣常臭　鬼魅所著　貧窮下賤　爲人所使　多病<span style="color: #8B0000">痟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">痩</span>　無所依怙　雖親附人　人不在意(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 95.9.durbala~; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  79a20; </p>

