尋<b>卽</b>(xún jí)　“immediately; soon after that”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://尋"><b>尋</b></a>(xún), <a href="bword://尋便">尋便</a>(xún biàn), <a href="bword://尋復">尋復</a>(xún fù), <a href="bword://尋時">尋時</a>(xún shí); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.1289.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.38.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">5a9.佛説是《法華》　令衆歡喜已　<span style="color: #8B0000">尋</span><span style="color: #8B0000">卽</span>於是日　告於天、人衆：　“諸法實相義　已爲汝等説　我今於中夜　當入於涅槃　……”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://K">K</a>.  25.12; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  67a26; </p>

