疑網(yí wǎng)　“a net of doubt”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.517a(唐代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.1153.; <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">6b22.無漏諸羅漢　及求涅槃者　今皆墮<span style="color: #8B0000">疑</span><span style="color: #8B0000">網</span>　“佛何故説是？”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 34.13.saṃśaya-; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 68c26.疑; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">10a20.菩薩聞是法　<span style="color: #8B0000">疑</span><span style="color: #8B0000">網</span>皆已除　千二百羅漢　悉亦當作佛(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 57.11.kāṅkṣā~; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  72c21; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">10c17.我(<i>i.e. Śāriputra</i>)聞是法音　得所未曾有　心懷大歡喜　<span style="color: #8B0000">疑</span><span style="color: #8B0000">網</span>皆已除(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 61.7.kathaṃkathā~; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  73b20; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">11a23(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 63.8.-kāṅkṣā~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 74a5.狐疑)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">11b3(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 64.3.vicikitsā-; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 74b16.<b>邪疑</b>)</p>

