有漏(yǒu lòu)　“outflow, defilement, impurity”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://漏"><b>漏</b></a>(lòu), <a href="bword://無漏">無漏</a>(wú lòu); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 6.1162a(百喩經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.1033d(涅槃經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">46c18.一時，皆得須陀洹道、斯陀含道、阿那含道、阿羅漢道，盡<span style="text-decoration: underline">諸<span style="color: #8B0000">有</span><span style="color: #8B0000">漏</span></span>，於深禪定皆得自在，具八解脱(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 347.11.-<span style="text-decoration: underline">āsrava</span>~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 118a28.<span style="text-decoration: underline">諸漏</span>; </p>

有爲
有爲(yǒu wéi)　“constituted things”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 6.1159b(景德傳燈録); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.1024a(景德傳燈録); <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">37c10.(<i>bodhisattva</i>s)又復不行　上中下法　<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">有</span><span style="color: #8B0000">爲</span>無爲</span>　實不實法　亦不分別　是男是女　不得諸法　不知不見　是則名爲　菩薩行處(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 281.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">saṃskṛtâsaṃskṛta</span>~; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 108a21.<span style="text-decoration: underline">元元</span>(←無無[a misprint of the <i>Taisho</i> Edition]; <i>v.ll.</i> 無无[= G, J], 源源)<span style="text-decoration: underline">常供養</span>; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>.  165; ; </span></p>

