有無見(yǒu wú jiàn)　“(false) views about existence and nonexistence”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  6.1159.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  5.1032.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">12b6.是學、無學人亦各自以(<a href="bword://J">J</a>.  已)離我見及<span style="color: #8B0000">有</span><span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">見</span>等，謂得涅槃(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 71.2.-vibhavadṛṣṭi-; ＝ <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .-bhavadṛṣṭi-vibhavadṛṣṭi-; ＝ <a href="bword://D2">D2</a> <i>etc.</i> -bhavadṛṣṭi-vibhavadṛṣṭi-; <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>. 75a25.三世(?); </p>

