讚頌(zàn sòng)　“sings in praise”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  11.476.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.626.; <a href="bword://Krsh(1998)">Krsh(1998)</a> , s.v.; <span class="xr">cf. <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.297a.贊頌(三國志); ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">45c3.是善男子、善女人受持讀誦是經典者，………　則爲以佛舍利起七寶塔，………　衆鼓、伎樂、簫笛、箜篌、種種舞戲，以妙音聲歌唄<span style="color: #8B0000">讚</span><span style="color: #8B0000">頌</span>，則爲(<i><a href="bword://v.l">v.l</a>. </i> 爲已)於無量千萬億劫，作是供養已(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://K">K</a>.  338.12; not found at <a href="bword://Z">Z</a>.  117a20; </p>

